            "title": "滬指開市跌19點 深成指跌89點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地股市初段下滑，上證綜指以4106點開市，跌19點或0.48%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指開市報14158點，亦跌89點或0.63%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數跌20點或0.42%，開報4721點；創業板指數開市報3318點，跌31點或0.93%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15583829-%e6%bb%ac%e6%8c%87%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%e8%b7%8c19%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b7%b1%e6%88%90%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c89%e9%bb%9e",
