        {
            "title": "港股開市︱初段略回 恒指跌27點報26972點 攜程低開近15%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股開市初段略為回吐，恒生指數開市報26972點，跌27點或0.1%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數開報5875點，跌32點或0.55%；國企指數以9305點開市，跌10點或0.11%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">順豐控股(06936)與極兔速遞(01519)深化戰略合作，互相認購對方股份，各涉款近83億元。兩股今早齊高開，順豐開報36.3元，升2.66%；極兔開報12.15元，升3.49%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：順豐官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20240923_FI_source-web_SF-2-704.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：順豐官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20240923_FI_source-web_SF-2-704.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：順豐官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">藥明合聯(02268)以99%溢價全面收購東曜藥業(01875)，並擬維持後者上市地位。兩股今早表現迥異，藥明合聯開報74元，跌2.31%；東曜藥業復牌以 元開市，彈升58.8%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">康龍化成(03795)折讓約8.5%配股籌逾13億元；該股今早開報24.1元，跌3.37%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：攜程官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250429_FI_source-web_09961.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：攜程官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250429_FI_source-web_09961.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：攜程官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">攜程(09961)涉壟斷遭市場監管總局立案調查，該股今早急挫14.98%，以484.2元開市。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15583818-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e7%95%a5%e5%9b%9e-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c27%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b126972%e9%bb%9e-%e6%94%9c%e7%a8%8b%e4%bd%8e%e9%96%8b%e8%bf%9115",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-15 09:30:29",
            "source": "bastillepost",
